{
  "id": "68f99196208d16db0d9674d1",
  "title": "成功した実写化の作品",
  "created": 1761186200,
  "updated": 1779177433,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "68f99196208d16db0d9674d1",
      "text": "成功した実写化の作品",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761186200,
      "updated": 1761186200
    },
    {
      "id": "68f97a180000000000be1f58",
      "text": "　[失敗した実写化の作品]",
      "userId": "67026b2a4d8cae001d9e390a",
      "created": 1761186283,
      "updated": 1761186295
    },
    {
      "id": "68f97a460000000000be1f5c",
      "text": "　意識したことないけども、地上波ドラマは成功してもしなくても原作が意識されることはあまりないイメージ[zatto.icon]",
      "userId": "67026b2a4d8cae001d9e390a",
      "created": 1761186329,
      "updated": 1761186333
    },
    {
      "id": "68f97a460000000000be1f5d",
      "text": "　　ジャンルの問題？",
      "userId": "67026b2a4d8cae001d9e390a",
      "created": 1761186329,
      "updated": 1761186340
    },
    {
      "id": "68f97af90000000000be1f61",
      "text": "　2.5次元ミュージカルはまた実写化とは別ジャンルか[zatto.icon]",
      "userId": "67026b2a4d8cae001d9e390a",
      "created": 1761186508,
      "updated": 1761186556
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9930400000000000e8b00",
      "text": "　\t映像作品前提とは考えてないから記載しても大丈夫だと思われ[QWOP.icon]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761186564,
      "updated": 1761186601
    },
    {
      "id": "68f97a180000000000be1f59",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "67026b2a4d8cae001d9e390a",
      "created": 1761186283,
      "updated": 1761186283
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9933500000000000e8b01",
      "text": "映像作品",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761186614,
      "updated": 1761186617
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9919800000000000e8aef",
      "text": " [DEATH NOTE]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761186200,
      "updated": 1761186253
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9919800000000000e8af0",
      "text": " [亜人]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761186200,
      "updated": 1761186248
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9919800000000000e8af1",
      "text": " [銀魂]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761186200,
      "updated": 1761186243
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9919800000000000e8af2",
      "text": "　[クローズZERO]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761186200,
      "updated": 1761186240
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9919800000000000e8af3",
      "text": " [トランスフォーマー]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761186200,
      "updated": 1761186238
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9919800000000000e8af4",
      "text": "　[バクマン(映画)]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761186200,
      "updated": 1761186234
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9919800000000000e8af5",
      "text": " [るろうに剣心]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761186200,
      "updated": 1761186230
    },
    {
      "id": "68f996dc00000000000e8b18",
      "text": " \t全5作",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761187549,
      "updated": 1761187555
    },
    {
      "id": "68f991a100000000000e8af8",
      "text": " [『白夜行』]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761186209,
      "updated": 1761186224
    },
    {
      "id": "68f991f000000000000e8af9",
      "text": " \t2006年のドラマ",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761186288,
      "updated": 1761186300
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9bc58000000000012e73a",
      "text": " \t韓国ドラマ化・映画化もしている",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761197145,
      "updated": 1761197161
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9921a00000000000e8afa",
      "text": " [クロサギ]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761186331,
      "updated": 1761186338
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9922900000000000e8afb",
      "text": " [医龍]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761186346,
      "updated": 1761186351
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9919a00000000000e8af7",
      "text": "　[のだめカンタービレ]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761186202,
      "updated": 1761186371
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9966f00000000000e8b17",
      "text": "　\tアニメ版もあり",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761187440,
      "updated": 1761187451
    },
    {
      "id": "68f97a970000000000be1f5e",
      "text": "　[ライアーゲーム]",
      "userId": "67026b2a4d8cae001d9e390a",
      "created": 1761186411,
      "updated": 1761186417
    },
    {
      "id": "68f97a9e0000000000be1f5f",
      "text": "　　原作よりも先に最終回が来た",
      "userId": "67026b2a4d8cae001d9e390a",
      "created": 1761186417,
      "updated": 1761186479
    },
    {
      "id": "68f992df00000000000e8afe",
      "text": "　[ゆるキャン△]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761186528,
      "updated": 1761186541
    },
    {
      "id": "68f992ee00000000000e8aff",
      "text": "　\t拒否反応がでて見ていないが、周囲＋SNSでは好印象なイメージ[QWOP.icon]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761186542,
      "updated": 1761186669
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9939000000000000e8b05",
      "text": "　[電車男]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761186705,
      "updated": 1761186710
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9939700000000000e8b06",
      "text": "　\tドラマ版・映画版あり",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761186711,
      "updated": 1761186725
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9bb61000000000012e735",
      "text": "　[賭博黙示録カイジ]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761196897,
      "updated": 1761196903
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9bb62000000000012e736",
      "text": "\t\t映画が全3作",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761196899,
      "updated": 1761196921
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9bb78000000000012e737",
      "text": "\t\t\t3作目は個人的なんとも言えない[QWOP.icon]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761196921,
      "updated": 1761196941
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9bbd5000000000012e738",
      "text": "\t[翼の折れた天使たち]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761197013,
      "updated": 1761197019
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9bbf7000000000012e739",
      "text": "\t\tスペシャルドラマを見てから原作小説買った[QWOP.icon]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761197047,
      "updated": 1761197075
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08598300000000002364e0",
      "text": "\tMCU等アメコミ系は成功といえるだろう",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778932099,
      "updated": 1778932113
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08599700000000002364e1",
      "text": "\t 原作コミックと新作映画情報を照らし合わせて、なんのキャラクターをどうアレンジして登場させるのかといった予測がひとつのコンテンツとなっている。実写化する側のひとつのテーマでもあるだろう。",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778932120,
      "updated": 1778932189
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0b9c0c0000000000c37a17",
      "text": "\t[孤独のグルメ]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1779145740,
      "updated": 1779145747
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9923d00000000000e8afc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761186366,
      "updated": 1761186366
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9933e00000000000e8b02",
      "text": "[2.5次元ミュージカル]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761186622,
      "updated": 1761186625
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9933e00000000000e8b03",
      "text": "\t[テニスの王子様]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761186623,
      "updated": 1761186682
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0c14e50000000000095c78",
      "text": "  [テニミュ]の認知度が飛び抜けておかしい[zatsma.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779176678,
      "updated": 1779176681
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0c14e50000000000095c79",
      "text": "   [空耳]の存在は大きい",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779176678,
      "updated": 1779176695
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0c14e50000000000095c7a",
      "text": "    友人も空耳きっかけで[テニミュ]現場に行ってハマっていた",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779176678,
      "updated": 1779176681
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0c14e50000000000095c7b",
      "text": "   地味に原作自体が現役コンテンツでもある([新テニスの王子様])",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779176678,
      "updated": 1779176681
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0c14e50000000000095c7c",
      "text": "    本家とかアニメにミュージカルの要素がフィードバックされているのもある",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779176678,
      "updated": 1779176681
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0c137f0000000000095c46",
      "text": "\t[薄桜鬼]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779176320,
      "updated": 1779176324
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0c13cb0000000000095c47",
      "text": "\t[弱虫ペダル (舞台)]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779176396,
      "updated": 1779176418
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0c141a0000000000095c49",
      "text": "\t[忍たま乱太郎]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779176474,
      "updated": 1779176480
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0c13e80000000000095c48",
      "text": "\t[刀剣乱舞]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779176425,
      "updated": 1779176441
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0c14a40000000000095c4a",
      "text": "\t[サクラ大戦]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779176617,
      "updated": 1779176617
    },
    {
      "id": "68f996fc00000000000e8b1b",
      "text": " 作品単位で見ると良い舞台はいっぱいある",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1761187581,
      "updated": 1778932074
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0859690000000000eda7bb",
      "text": "  観劇層の母数がドラマや映画と比べて少ない",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778932074,
      "updated": 1778932074
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0858f70000000000eda7b9",
      "text": "  どこからが成功なのだろうと考えてしまう[zatsma.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778931960,
      "updated": 1778932002
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08596f0000000000eda7bc",
      "text": "   社会現象化しづらいジャンルと言える",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778932080,
      "updated": 1779176313
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0c12e80000000000095c45",
      "text": "  長く続いてるシリーズは商業的に成功していると考えていいだろう",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779176168,
      "updated": 1779176866
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0c15290000000000095c7d",
      "text": "   [長寿ジャンル]について追記した[zatsma.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779176746,
      "updated": 1779177433
    },
    {
      "id": "68f996fd00000000000e8b1c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761187581,
      "updated": 1761187581
    },
    {
      "id": "68f9937600000000000e8b04",
      "text": "[実写版映画・ドラマ]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761186678,
      "updated": 1761187579
    },
    {
      "id": "68f996fb00000000000e8b19",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1761187579,
      "updated": 1761187579
    }
  ]
}